Package com.facebook.buck.android.support.exopackage

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApplicationLike
    This interface is used to delegate calls from main Application object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultApplicationLike
    Empty implementation of ApplicationLike.
    ExopackageApplication<T extends ApplicationLike>
    A base class for implementing an Application that delegates to an ApplicationLike instance.
    ExopackageDexLoader
    Loads pre-dexed jars installed by the exopackage installer into our ClassLoader.
    ExopackageSoLoader
    Loads native library files installed by the exopackage installer.
